      "writtenOn": "2016-04-12T17:09:55Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "aargh, really? that sounds like a real bug here :(\n\nGenerally, I dislike the use of weak pointers, but it looks like it\u0027s clearly necessary here. Thanks.",
      "revId": "14c3a1bd44ac6f7a31a4accca63c0ea5e1308636",
      "serverId": "85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889",
